room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by ESCAPE:chandler in Phoenix
room_address: 312 N Alma School Rd, Suite 9, Chandler, AZ 85224
room_description:
Your camping vacation has turned bad. You wake up in the middle of the night and find one of your friends is missing. You follow a faint trail of blood to a remote cabin in the woods and soon discover something is horribly wrong there.
You try to call the police, but quickly realize you have no phone service this deep in the woods.
